---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Rainbow Root Veggies with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Crispy, crunchy, and oh-so-satisfying! This golden crumbed chicken is paired with hearty root veggies, tossed with buttery silverbeet. Topped with a creamy pesto dressing, this dish is the ultimate cosy meal for your taste buds!
